{"tid":313323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家啲小學生圍內都講煲冬瓜？！","createTime":"2017-07-08T08:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T10:40:16.000Z","uid":57308,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dced7d39a3feff8e8d8c6c9dbd76f30a400a5687","tid":313323,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:44:08.000Z","msg":"頭先落美心食西多屎，前面排左幾個小學下，去叫野食同個美心姐姐都係講廣東話(冇鄉音) <br />\n之後排隊拎野食，佢地傾計竟然係煲冬瓜為主，夾雜啲廣東話咁<br />\n香港細路究竟發生緊咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14748b9c7c2b8d32e8a5b1728c63657673d8ba39","tid":313323,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"唔知<br />\n一入天水圍啲小朋友全部講普通話<br />\n搭地鐵又係<br />\n痴撚線"},{"pid":"6aa8830f88ecb4cb9d0fef27cdc33a97abb86cca","tid":313323,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"普教中已經開始左<br />\n我都係近排先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e552e6d1c9d6b4646b023cfd49a05da1aec23e","tid":313323,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:46:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知<br />\n一入天水圍啲小朋友全部講普通話<br />\n搭地鐵又係<br />\n痴撚線</blockquote><br />\n我指小學生<br />\n元朗區又係，中學生都普通話"},{"pid":"7f6d3f4216d7e5af29f445881b06b7b6daf29e5b","tid":313323,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:49:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb1dd7ba0194b62e68a997a936f5b26c523748b3","tid":313323,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:49:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普教中已經開始左<br />\n我都係近排先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開始咗好耐"},{"pid":"88c63a171a5eded90c294f8d431b794a4d72fcf0","tid":313323,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知<br />\n一入天水圍啲小朋友全部講普通話<br />\n搭地鐵又係<br />\n痴撚線</blockquote><br />\n有時撞正放學時間行過觀塘區啲中小學，講